sols.text: ماذا تحب أن تفعل في وقت فراغك؟
What do you like to do in your free time?
I like to ski. What about you?
أنا لا أحب أن أرقص على الإطلاق.
I don't like to dance at all.
I'm not very good at it.
It's not that hard, you'll see.
And do you have any other hobbies?
Me too. What are you reading now?
مشوق. أنا أحب كتب التاريخ أكثر.
Interesting. I like history books more.
إذن هل تريد الانضمام إلى نادي الكتاب لدينا؟
Then do you want to join our book club?
Perfect. Our next meeting is on Friday.
